description: "This mid-18th century map of Celebes (Sulawasi) shows the island divided into approximately a dozen separate kingdoms. The Gulf of Saleyer is noted as being ‘rempli de Bancs de Sable [filled with sandbanks]’."
label: "De Moluccos en andere Speceri-Eilanden in d' Oost-Indien / door Pierre van der Aa."
